title: Denton Vegan Cooperative
description: A workers' cooperative with a booth at the Denton Community Market, an open air market held Saturdays May to October until 1pm. The co-op makes baked goods like banana breads and muffins, and street foods such as nachos and ice cream. All 100% vegan. Also sold at Jupiter House coffee shops and Vegan Freak store.
streetAddress: Carroll Blvd and W Mulberry St
